 /2024/06/Art-Venture-Dress-Up.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy Art Venture with FREE admission thanks to our friends at
  Brain Injury Solutions!\n\nFor this Free Art Venture Day\, experience all
  of the stations in our interactive gallery including special projects tha
 t celebrate arts and culture in southwest Virginia!\n\nVisitors to Art Ven
 ture can paint\, draw\, build\, connect music with art\, investigate 3D pr
 inting and printmaking\, create sculptures\, display artwork\, and much mo
 re. Stations are designed to engage families and children.\n\nThe Museum i
 s also pleased to share the new exhibition\, LeUyen Came Along: The Art of
  LeUyen Pham featuring the work of the beloved children’s illustrator be
 hind such classic series as “Itty-Bitty Kitty Corn\,” “Vampirina Bal
 lerina\,” “Bear Came Along\,” and more. This exhibition is also free
  and welcoming to all.\n\nNo registration required – walk-in’s welcome
 !\n\nSource: https://www.taubmanmuseum.org/free-art-venture-march-21
