SUMMARY:Mokha Laget: Mural Title TBD
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260418T000000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20280611T235959
UID:10001950-1776470400-1844380799@www.taubmanmuseum.org
DESCRIPTION:Source: https://www.taubmanmuseum.org/event/mokha-laget-mural-
 title-tbd/
